1. Collect potential customer information from channels such as Google,
, LinkedIn, and customs data;

2. Independently develop new clients;

3. Create and maintain customer contact records, and provide regular feedback to the company through weekly reports.

Requirements:

1. Proficiency in Google Search: Ability to accurately locate target customers’ official websites, key contacts,
 addresses, phone numbers, and other relevant information;

2. Excellent English skills: Strong reading and writing abilities, along with fluent oral communication. Must be capable of communicating proficiently with foreign clients via
, voice calls, video conferences, etc.;

3. Strong comprehension and communication skills: Ability to quickly understand clients’ businesses, products, and needs;

4. Fast learner: Able to acquire new knowledge quickly and work effectively under a certain level of pressure;

5. Work five days a week, from Monday to Friday.Eight hours per day,Working hours: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM and 1:00 PM – 6:00 PM (GMT+8).
